haiku:
Illicit lotus
Chili mango, jicama
This lake has secrets.

This sushi is good
if it is not too much trouble
May i have some more?

Maps are really cool
Pico Union is my hood
this neighborhoods dope

like moths to the flame
the mothership beckoning
GIS HQ

NOT WeHo at all
But a subway churro gal
It's all here today

So quiet
Nothing to do
Sleepy little hamlet.

大风起兮云飞扬，
威加海内兮归故乡，
安得猛士兮守四方？

Palm fronds
We're getting Expo
Indian food rocks!

we learning to map
in downtown los angeles
arup is the place!

I am not from here
I miss San Diego tons
Home is where heart is

herons, humans, bunnies
paletas and taco stands
what else do you need?

Is this Covina
Or is this West Covina?
Please incorporate.

Middle of nowhere.
Behold! Craft beer exists here.
A bright oasis.

A Shanghai treasure--
Crispy bottom, burst of soup.
This is sheng jian bao.

A mom and pop shop,
Kabob with your techno dance.
Yogurt drink? Say no.

County hearts die here
Lost in a cubicle sea
Windowless. Soul-less.

Barricades go up
We are prepping for the siege
Rose Parade Cometh!
